OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,FVicki Lindsay and Emma Webber have
OL,7,Fcome together to campaign for stronger
OL,8,Fvictims' rights, as ITV News' Ben
OL,9,FChapman reports
OL,11,FWords by ITV News Senior Producer Cat
OL,12,FDinneny
OL,14,FTwo women whose loved ones were killed
OL,15,Fby paranoid schizophrenics have
OL,16,Fdemanded more rights for victims over
OL,17,Ffears they will be excluded from
OL,18,Fdecisions concerning offenders.
