OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,FEmma Webber, whose son Barnaby was
OL,7,Fkilled in Nottingham in 2023, and
OL,8,FVicki Lindsay, whose step-father Lewis
OL,9,FStone was killed in Mid Wales in 2019,
OL,10,Fare calling for the Victims and Courts
OL,11,FBill to be strengthened.
OL,13,FAs the bill stands, victims will have
OL,14,Fno statutory rights to be told about
OL,15,Fdecisions affecting the detention,
OL,16,Fleave, or discharge of mentally
OL,17,Fdisordered offenders unless the
OL,18,Fauthorities 'consider it appropriate'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
