OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,FThe two have come together after Mr
OL,7,FStone's killer, David Fleet, was
OL,8,Fgranted permission to leave hospital
OL,9,Fearlier this year; a decision Vicki
OL,10,Fand her family were not told about.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News, Vicki said:
OL,13,F"It's been six years of hell for the
OL,14,Fwhole family."
OL,16,FLewis Stone was repeatedly stabbed by
OL,17,FFleet in a random attack as he walked
OL,18,Fhis dog near his holiday home in Borth
OL,19,Fin February 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
