OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,FFleet, who has schizophrenia, had been
OL,7,Freleased from a secure psychiatric
OL,8,Funit just 10 days before the incident.
OL,10,FHe admitted manslaughter by diminished
OL,11,Fresponsibility and was given an
OL,12,Findefinite hospital order.
OL,14,FBut earlier this year, just six years
OL,15,Finto his sentence, Fleet was allowed
OL,16,Fovernight leave from the secure unit.
OL,18,FVicki said: "The ball started rolling
OL,19,Fthree years after the incident to get
OL,20,Fhim escorted leave, so we knew
OL,21,Funescorted leave would eventually come.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
