OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,F"We should have had a lot more input.
OL,7,FWe should have been the first port of
OL,8,Fcall."
OL,10,FShe added: "I'm angry, scared. In my
OL,11,Fheart of hearts, I just feel it's
OL,12,Fgoing to happen again. Another family
OL,13,Fis going to go through what we've gone
OL,14,Fthrough."
OL,16,FThe decision to grant Fleet leave
OL,17,Fwithout any input from Mr Stone's
OL,18,Ffamily is exactly what Emma Webber
OL,19,Ffears could happen with her son's
OL,20,Fkiller, Valdo Calocane.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
