OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,FCalocane, who also has schizophrenia,
OL,7,Fstabbed university students Barnaby
OL,8,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar and
OL,9,Fcaretaker Ian Coates in June 2023. He
OL,10,Fwas given an indefinite hospital order
OL,11,Fafter pleading guilty to manslaughter
OL,12,Fwith diminished responsibility.
OL,14,FEmma said: "The thought of that
OL,15,Fmonster being allowed out, you fear it
OL,16,Fhappening again. We plan on doing
OL,17,Fabsolutely everything we can to
OL,18,Fprevent that happening, but as it
OL,19,Fstands at the moment, it's inevitable."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
