OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,FThe Victims and Courts Bill aims to
OL,7,Fimprove the experience of victims
OL,8,Fwithin the criminal justice system. It
OL,9,Fincludes provisions to compel
OL,10,Foffenders to attend their sentencing
OL,11,Fand bolster the powers of the Victims'
OL,12,FCommissioner.
OL,14,FBut campaigners, including Vicki and
OL,15,FEmma, are concerned about the
OL,16,Fdiscretion that will be given to
OL,17,Fprobation officers and hospital
OL,18,Fmanagers about what information is
OL,19,Fshared with victims where offenders
OL,20,Fare serving hospital orders rather
OL,21,Fthan prison sentences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
