OL,3,CVictims' families come together to
OL,4,Cdemand stronger rights
OL,6,FThey fear they will be isolated from
OL,7,Fdecisions concerning an offender's
OL,8,Fleave or discharge from hospital and
OL,9,Fare calling for parity with the parole
OL,10,Fsystem, where victims have the right
OL,11,Fto be informed, consulted and can
OL,12,Fchallenge decisions.
OL,14,F"It's abhorrent," Emma said. "Where
OL,15,Fare the rights? Where is the dignity
OL,16,Fand the rights in the victims in all
OL,17,Fof this?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
