OL,6,FA government spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,FVictims and Courts Bill will ensure
OL,8,Fall victims can request important
OL,9,Finformation about an offender
OL,10,Fregardless of whether they're in
OL,11,Fprison or hospital. We will continue
OL,12,Fto engage with victims and campaigners
OL,13,Fas the bill moves through Parliament."
OL,15,FEmma and Vicki have been invited to a
OL,16,Fmeeting with the Victims Minister,
OL,17,FAlex Davies-Jones, to discuss their
OL,18,Fconcerns.
